{"tid":729273,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"二手居屋減價20萬！天盛苑未補價400萬沽","createTime":"2018-07-04T11:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T12:31:31.000Z","uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"af99ac78409f24a435e222cbc3426752cc297b63","tid":729273,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180704/photo/bkn-20180704184136677-0704_00842_001_01p.jpg?20180704192801\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180704%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180704184136677-0704_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20180704192801&h=44fa45d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新居屋加大折扣，未補價第二市場二手業主減價沽貨。祥益黃慶德稱，天水圍居屋天盛苑R座高層8室，實用面積506方呎，於上星期政府出招前叫價420萬元放盤，到出招後連減兩口價共20萬元，未補價終售400萬元，呎價7,905元。"},{"pid":"eec562af74c8782d283fa3b3d12fa70c08363d3e","tid":729273,"uid":186543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:01:27.000Z","msg":"天水圍都400萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貪新移民人妻多咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd1dbc9431c8de4871d520a989dbac393cbf752","tid":729273,"uid":166792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"506 400萬 天水圍 居屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad88e6c191720936072d1e6470a6ba78adc3a412","tid":729273,"uid":865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eec562af74c8782d283fa3b3d12fa70c08363d3e","tid":729273,"uid":186543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy"